       <h2 class="forums"><a href="/forums">Knowledge Base</a><span class="delim">/</span><a href="/categories/20136583-Product-Updates-and-Announcements">Product Updates and Announcements</a><span class="delim">/</span><a href="/forums/23071646-What-s-New-at-Issuu">What's New at Issuu</a></h2> 
       <div class="frame"> 
        <div class="entry nobottom" style="padding-bottom:0;"> 
         <h3 class="entry-title" style="padding-bottom: 9px;">Introducing the new Publisher Tools page</h3> 
         <img src="/system/photos/0001/2203/9718/issuuIcon_80x80_thumb.png" class="entry_user"> 
         <div class="entry-container"> 
          <p class="entry_user"> Denise T.<br> posted this on August 19, 2014, 09:49 </p> 
          <div class="share_button_container"> 
           <ul class="share_buttons"> 
            <li class="linkedin_button"> <script src="//platform.linkedin.com/in.js" type="text/javascript"></script> <script type="IN/Share" data-url="http://help.issuu.com/entries/97502366-Introducing-the-new-Publisher-Tools-page" data-counter="right"></script> </li> 
            <li class="twitter_button"> <a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="http://help.issuu.com/entries/97502366-Introducing-the-new-Publisher-Tools-page" data-counturl="http://help.issuu.com/entries/97502366-Introducing-the-new-Publisher-Tools-page" data-text="Introducing the new Publisher Tools page" data-lang="en" data-count="horizontal">Tweet</a><script type="text/javascript" src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js"></script> </li> 
            <li class="facebook_button"> <iframe src="//www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3A%2F%2Fhelp.issuu.com%2Fentries%2F97502366-Introducing-the-new-Publisher-Tools-page&amp;send=false&amp;layout=button_count&amp;show_faces=false&amp;action=like&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;font=arial&amp;locale=en_US" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true"></iframe> </li> 
           </ul> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
         <div class="user_formatted header_section clearfix"> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Today, &nbsp;we’re introducing a new way of viewing your Publications on Issuu. “My Publications” in the top navigation bar is now "Publisher Tools". This updated page will now give publishers a new list-view of all their publications, with easier navigation to edit and share your publications. We created this simpler, more </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">intuitive page to give publishers the tools to publish and edit their work on Issuu quickly and efficiently.</span></p> 
          <p><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></strong></p> 
          <p style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><img src="/attachments/token/odl2mAKQXpQpOLQxS9aihhsCX/?name=MyPublications-Now_Publisher_Tools.png" alt="MyPublications-Now_Publisher_Tools.png" width="727" height="92"></strong></strong></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">&nbsp;</p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">You can now easily reach the actions that are most important to you - edit, share, embed, download - and make your publications the best they can be from within the Publications page. Here's a brief summary of what you can expect with the new "Publisher Tools" page of your Issuu account.</span></p> 
          <h2 style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Default List View</span></em></span></h2> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Your publications will always be shown as a list, to make it easier for you to browse through them. &nbsp;You can also now order by publication status (scheduled, quarantined or unlisted), upload date, or original publishing date. You can also use our new dynamic search to search your entire archive for a particular publication.</span></p> 
          <p><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></strong></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 13px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/6LjuQu0EuGjN2rGpcVqtLtcxln8wpeSPW3gbjAB656GSGgUEUAVtyXUic8ox2qdCHM59pOlKCfLFjLqJWdyLYZV3P7wbrO0h_VEW3YK_IT0XLxHzNXBKcAmY9stfqz-utQ" alt="NewPubSuite2.png" width="620px;" height="251px;"></span></p> 
          <p><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></strong></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 13px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/Li1yr1NAO805V_rxsyGRnDyGnLfEFJHvVmBthoPoysczRpfu3zXbWBuoiQtVg7_jiFfdJeVEzL5JkqVZQh0UjafROMA-Oq5iKYRmcFgOaE864F7Bga3knA-sip3xgGneGg" alt="NewPubSuite1.png" width="625px;" height="274px;"></span></p> 
          <p><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></strong></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">NOTE:</span> This ability to order/sort your publications can only be seen by you the publisher. Organizing/Reordering of publications on your public profile is still being worked on at the moment.</span></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">&nbsp;</p> 
          <h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: underline;">Perform Bulk Operations on all your publications</span></em></span></h2> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">You can now select multiple publications to publish, add to a stack, or delete using the check-boxes to the left of the list followed by one of the action buttons above the publications list.</span></p> 
          <p><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></strong></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: 13px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img src="/attachments/token/bwoYYZ61cOXmDLJQ1qInDyc2q/?name=NewPubSuite3.png" alt="NewPubSuite3.png" width="657" height="471"></span></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">&nbsp;</p> 
          <p><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></strong></p> 
          <h2 style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">One click to Share, Embed and More</span></span></em></h2> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Instead of multiple actions and menus, hovering over the arrow button to the right of a publication will give you a drop-down contextual menu with direct access to your Issuu must-haves: <a href="http://help.issuu.com/entries/40675833-How-can-I-share-my-publication-after-uploading-to-Issuu-" target="_blank">share</a>, <a href="http://help.issuu.com/entries/23965637-How-to-embed-Issuu-on-your-website-for-publishers-" target="_blank">embed</a>, <a href="http://help.issuu.com/entries/23971538-Can-I-download-and-or-print-a-publication-" target="_blank">download</a> and more.</span></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">&nbsp;</p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">You can also jump straight to the <a href="http://help.issuu.com/forums/23037413-Statistics-on-Issuu" target="_blank">Statistics</a> dashboard for any publication, purchase <a href="http://help.issuu.com/forums/22146568-Targeted-Distribution" target="_blank">Targeted Distribution</a>, and order a physical print with our <a href="http://help.issuu.com/forums/22906628-Publisher-Print-On-Demand" target="_blank">Publisher Print On Demand</a> program.</span></p> 
          <p><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></strong></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 13px; font-family: Arial; color: #272727; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/EFpkvOMxJg6g3T1nJVH-d4SU9IT1OSZJkwfqpTSAftfM1oVWpBf6HhxUU_14uXzIjjU4ggH8PtWEYxKnIeI570LZP9MH5VHclj3A5E7U1RQwOTJbcKUY4kQHR2L4RZ7HcQ" alt="NewPubSuite4.png" width="514px;" height="367px;"></span></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">&nbsp;</p> 
          <p><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></strong></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">&nbsp;</p> 
          <h2 style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Easy Access to editing tools</span></em></span></h2> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">With this simpler interface, you only need to select “Edit” from the drop-down menu to edit a specific publication’s document settings, embed widget, and access the link editor. </span></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">&nbsp;</p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">After making and saving your changes, use the blue “Back to Publications List” button at the bottom of the page to get back to the full list of your Publications.</span></p> 
          <p><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></strong></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 13px; font-family: Arial; color: #272727; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/_GF2Gvu0W0y1bT3PyErhdSZ05U8NNmfkgIoMNzfBqTIO0eq7kd3Fr3klf5fJxW0lYotu0jEUDN7YR3WOG9bXUVWdDgj3FbQdwWH8X-jfw6QpXUXrzczjmHNUgOtkpV6mVg" alt="NewPubSuite5.png" width="720px;" height="540px;"></span></p> 
          <p><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><strong style="font-weight: normal;"><br><br><br></strong></strong></p> 
          <p style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">With this new publications list, you’ll be able to manage your publications with ease so that you can spend more time doing what you do best: creating world-class publications.</span></p> 
